cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with active learning using deep neural network models, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, since the paper focuses on batch active learning with deep neural network models, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.AI and cs.CV.
